sources.description:
Eenie Meenie Miney Moe (EM3) - Drugs and grand theft auto, Raul lives his life on the edge. Faced with the painful choice between love and riches, Raul makes a shocking choice, blinded by the nightclub lights. A thrilling first-person view through the eyes of a drug dealer. It is Miami, but it may well be LA, NY, Atlanta, Chicago, Dallas or anyone's backyard, where hustlers play and the game has no rules.
2013.  Stars: Andres Dominguez, Belkys Galvez, David Scott Lago
